00:09:14.840 --> 00:09:15.700
Your Highness,

00:09:16.480 --> 00:09:18.210
Prince Li's true target is you.

00:09:18.360 --> 00:09:19.290
He took my people

00:09:19.410 --> 00:09:20.790
just to show you his power.

00:09:20.790 --> 00:09:21.670
If you go,

00:09:22.000 --> 00:09:23.370
you'll be walking right into his trap.

00:09:23.370 --> 00:09:24.430
I'm going this time

00:09:24.670 --> 00:09:25.510
with nothing to do

00:09:25.510 --> 00:09:26.510
with the Li family

00:09:26.510 --> 00:09:27.710
or the Changfeng Army.

00:09:27.710 --> 00:09:29.110
I represent only myself.

