Kill him.

00:11:48.160 --> 00:11:49.690
Who really deserves to die?

00:11:55.830 --> 00:11:56.830
Qiao...

00:11:59.960 --> 00:12:00.790
Qiao.

00:12:13.760 --> 00:12:14.670
Let her go.

00:12:15.020 --> 00:12:16.880
I heard you possess miraculous power,

00:12:16.880 --> 00:12:19.510
able to defeat more than
10,000 Yao Army soldiers on your own.

00:12:19.510 --> 00:12:21.600
I suppose Li Shuang dares oppose me

00:12:21.790 --> 00:12:23.670
only because she has you to rely on.

00:12:23.670 --> 00:12:24.930
If you want her to live,

00:12:25.440 --> 00:12:27.500
you'd better surrender obediently.

00:12:28.940 --> 00:12:29.580
Go.

00:12:31.150 --> 00:12:32.110
Go!

00:12:32.110 --> 00:12:33.510
No, we won't leave!

00:12:33.510 --> 00:12:33.840
We won't go!

00:12:33.840 --> 00:12:34.550
Qiao!

00:12:35.270 --> 00:12:35.910
Qiao!

00:12:35.910 --> 00:12:36.670
We won't go!

00:12:36.670 --> 00:12:37.240
Qiao!

00:12:37.240 --> 00:12:38.200
Qiao!

00:12:38.200 --> 00:12:39.120
Qiao!

00:13:12.280 --> 00:13:13.280
Su Muli.

00:13:15.460 --> 00:13:17.660
The worst mistake you ever made

00:13:19.010 --> 00:13:21.010
was taking me as your hostage.

00:13:22.750 --> 00:13:23.550
Qiao!

00:13:23.570 --> 00:13:24.340
Qiao!

00:13:25.830 --> 00:13:27.190
Qiao!

00:13:43.730 --> 00:13:45.770
Jin'an...

00:13:47.280 --> 00:13:48.040
Don't...

00:13:48.480 --> 00:13:49.210
kill...

00:13:49.230 --> 00:13:50.990
him.

00:13:52.790 --> 00:13:57.590
Keep the General safe.

00:13:59.010 --> 00:14:00.130
Qiao.

